OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy night with a few clear
OL,7,Fspells possible. Breezy to start but
OL,8,Fwinds falling light later. Mild,
OL,9,Fthough warm in towns and cities.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FDry and bright with a light
OL,12,Fbreeze. Plenty of hazy sunshine and
OL,13,Fsunny spells at times. Another hot
OL,14,Fday, similar to Monday.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,17,Fand sunny to end the week. Light
OL,18,Fwinds, though breezier Friday. Hot
OL,19,Fthroughout as temperatures increase.
